WEBVTT

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:33.280
[You Have My Heart]

00:00:33.310 --> 00:00:36.340
[Episode 16 Want Real Gold]

00:00:41.750 --> 00:00:43.390
Wu Youdao.

00:00:50.350 --> 00:00:53.600
I've seen through your misfortune.

00:00:54.240 --> 00:00:58.030
If you seek real gold,
you must sign a void contract.

00:00:59.670 --> 00:01:00.520
Who are you?

00:01:02.110 --> 00:01:03.430
Whoever you prayed to—

00:01:04.280 --> 00:01:05.640
then that's who I am.

00:01:07.430 --> 00:01:09.490
You're the Fortune-Turning Master?

00:01:11.480 --> 00:01:13.410
Are you here to turn my luck around?

00:02:37.060 --> 00:02:38.320
My Lord, you're awake.

00:02:38.680 --> 00:02:40.120
You finally got some sleep last night,

00:02:40.120 --> 00:02:41.400
I didn't dare disturb you,

00:02:41.400 --> 00:02:43.130
so I just brought you a blanket.

00:02:43.310 --> 00:02:45.110
That was very thoughtful of you.

00:02:45.150 --> 00:02:45.870
My Lord,

00:02:46.030 --> 00:02:47.240
the water for washing is ready,

00:02:47.240 --> 00:02:48.680
and the meal is prepared as well.

00:02:48.680 --> 00:02:50.079
I'll get back to work now.

00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:52.800
Shuan,

00:02:52.800 --> 00:02:54.260
you're so diligent today.

00:02:55.150 --> 00:02:56.910
His Lordship has been unwell lately,

00:02:56.910 --> 00:02:59.310
a cleaner county yamen
might help clear his mind.

00:02:59.310 --> 00:03:00.960
But you don't have to scrub
between the bricks.

00:03:00.960 --> 00:03:02.310
It's going to take forever!

00:03:02.310 --> 00:03:02.960
My Lord,

00:03:03.240 --> 00:03:04.800
This is a herbal remedy
for a cold that I got

00:03:04.800 --> 00:03:06.430
specifically from an old physician
at the south end of the village.

00:03:06.430 --> 00:03:07.780
Drink it while it's hot.

00:03:07.960 --> 00:03:08.750
Thank you.

00:03:23.310 --> 00:03:24.590
With the sudden drop in temperature,

00:03:24.590 --> 00:03:26.800
we can't delay resettling
the beggars and refugees.

00:03:26.800 --> 00:03:27.930
Let's go take a look.

00:03:39.520 --> 00:03:39.910
Take this.

00:03:39.910 --> 00:03:40.800
It's my turn.

00:03:40.800 --> 00:03:41.400
Thank you.

00:03:42.680 --> 00:03:43.340
Get in line.

00:03:44.430 --> 00:03:46.190
Xiqianhua is truly generous.

00:03:46.520 --> 00:03:46.960
My Lord,

00:03:46.960 --> 00:03:49.240
those are all brand new
padded coats and blankets.

00:03:49.240 --> 00:03:52.300
They are much better
than our county yamen's supplies.

00:03:53.800 --> 00:03:54.600
Look, My Lord.

00:03:54.960 --> 00:03:56.560
I told you that
you were worrying too much.

00:03:56.560 --> 00:03:59.000
We have Lady Fufeng
personally overseeing this.

00:03:59.000 --> 00:04:00.660
There's enough for everyone.

00:04:02.120 --> 00:04:02.870
Over here.

00:04:04.240 --> 00:04:05.000
Thank you.

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:06.470
There's enough for everyone.

00:04:06.470 --> 00:04:07.270
Here, take it.

00:04:09.150 --> 00:04:10.000
You're welcome.

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:11.330
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

00:04:12.030 --> 00:04:13.230
There's plenty more.

00:04:13.680 --> 00:04:15.000
Don't spill it.

00:04:24.190 --> 00:04:25.000
Hu,

00:04:25.800 --> 00:04:26.600
go over there.

00:04:41.510 --> 00:04:43.310
-Here.
-Thank you, My Lord.

00:04:47.750 --> 00:04:48.800
Here, try some.

00:04:49.830 --> 00:04:51.480
Thank you, My Lord.

00:04:53.830 --> 00:04:54.430
My Lord.

00:04:55.159 --> 00:04:56.800
Thank you, My Lord.

00:05:35.040 --> 00:05:37.830
Thank you, Lady Fufeng.

00:05:39.870 --> 00:05:41.120
Come here, everyone.

00:05:41.190 --> 00:05:42.240
Please line up.

00:05:42.430 --> 00:05:44.430
Lord Bai of the county yamen

00:05:44.560 --> 00:05:46.510
prepared these especially for all of you.

00:05:46.510 --> 00:05:47.920
Even with such poor health, you are still

00:05:47.920 --> 00:05:49.240
out here taking care of the people.

00:05:49.240 --> 00:05:50.390
Everyone gets one.

00:05:50.800 --> 00:05:53.040
Since you've entrusted this matter to me,

00:05:53.040 --> 00:05:54.190
why are you here now?

00:05:55.830 --> 00:05:58.430
Were you afraid
I wouldn't handle it properly?

00:06:01.980 --> 00:06:04.540
You always handle things well,
Lady Fufeng.

00:06:05.270 --> 00:06:08.560
It's just that this is my duty.

00:06:09.000 --> 00:06:10.720
If I didn't come see for myself,

00:06:10.720 --> 00:06:11.920
I wouldn't be at ease.

00:06:15.430 --> 00:06:17.430
You didn't talk to me when you saw me.

00:06:18.310 --> 00:06:21.430
Are you still upset with me
for taking your heart?

00:06:32.040 --> 00:06:32.830
I...

00:06:34.240 --> 00:06:35.970
I gave my heart back willingly.

00:06:36.400 --> 00:06:38.000
Why would I be upset with you?

00:06:39.170 --> 00:06:41.850
It's only that you looked so busy,

00:06:41.880 --> 00:06:43.340
I didn't dare disturb you.

00:06:50.770 --> 00:06:51.659
Bai Shanjun.

00:06:53.080 --> 00:06:54.480
You're not good at lying.

00:06:58.870 --> 00:06:59.360
I...

00:07:00.610 --> 00:07:03.570
My mind is so clouded with thoughts.

00:07:04.190 --> 00:07:06.430
And I can't even sort them out myself.

00:07:08.270 --> 00:07:09.600
I don't know how

00:07:10.430 --> 00:07:12.030
to face you anymore, My Lady.

00:07:59.820 --> 00:08:00.820
Quiet, look!

00:08:00.840 --> 00:08:03.040
There are new clothes and steamed buns!

00:08:03.430 --> 00:08:04.190
Quiet?

00:08:04.430 --> 00:08:05.270
It's alright, take your time.

00:08:05.270 --> 00:08:06.930
There's enough for everyone.

00:08:08.880 --> 00:08:09.810
Someone's dead!

00:08:10.120 --> 00:08:11.050
Someone's dead!

00:08:12.720 --> 00:08:13.350
Someone's dead!

00:08:13.350 --> 00:08:14.720
Hu, secure the scene.

00:08:14.800 --> 00:08:15.680
Everyone, step back.

00:08:15.680 --> 00:08:17.270
County yamen is on duty, do not disturb.

00:08:17.270 --> 00:08:17.830
Please don't crowd together.

00:08:17.830 --> 00:08:18.430
Step back.

00:08:26.570 --> 00:08:28.770
He has been dead for more than half a day.

00:08:29.070 --> 00:08:30.200
He was likely pierced through

00:08:30.200 --> 00:08:33.600
the heart and lungs by
a bamboo pole last night, dying from it.

00:08:34.510 --> 00:08:36.870
There's no lingering evil power here,

00:08:37.270 --> 00:08:39.200
and this wasn't the work of a demon.

00:08:45.120 --> 00:08:47.600
How could nobody notice

00:08:48.550 --> 00:08:50.440
a poor beggar dying

00:08:50.670 --> 00:08:52.000
in such a crowded place?

00:08:52.440 --> 00:08:53.440
He... he was a mute.

00:08:53.440 --> 00:08:54.910
He usually slept here.

00:08:55.640 --> 00:08:57.390
What kind of monster would kill a beggar?

00:08:57.390 --> 00:08:58.000
Yeah.

00:08:58.440 --> 00:08:59.440
Silent, everyone.

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:00.870
Don't disturb Lord Bai's investigation.

00:09:00.870 --> 00:09:02.000
Lady Fufeng is still here.

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:03.260
What are you afraid of?

00:09:04.020 --> 00:09:05.380
Hu, take notes.

00:09:07.720 --> 00:09:09.960
Murder weapon: a piece of bamboo pole.

00:09:10.840 --> 00:09:11.720
Length:

00:09:13.240 --> 00:09:14.100
about 1.2 feet.

00:09:14.360 --> 00:09:17.020
It's slightly yellow in color,
hard in texture.

00:09:17.870 --> 00:09:18.330
My Lord.

00:09:19.190 --> 00:09:21.120
This bamboo pole looks pretty old.

00:09:21.440 --> 00:09:22.240
Right.

00:09:22.260 --> 00:09:23.600
Look at these marks here.

00:09:23.600 --> 00:09:24.960
There are some faint scratches.

00:09:24.960 --> 00:09:26.600
It must have been tied to

00:09:26.850 --> 00:09:28.850
or rubbed against some kind of tool.

00:09:46.960 --> 00:09:47.600
Is this...

00:09:50.860 --> 00:09:51.740
paste?

00:10:03.150 --> 00:10:03.630
My Lord.

00:10:03.910 --> 00:10:06.600
Are you here to buy
paper horses and figures?

00:10:07.030 --> 00:10:11.230
Our goods are made with care, perfect
for giving the dead a proper send-off.

00:10:12.080 --> 00:10:13.740
Are you the owner of this shop?

00:10:14.270 --> 00:10:15.080
Yes.

00:10:16.550 --> 00:10:18.150
We are from the county yamen.

00:10:21.670 --> 00:10:23.200
I wasn't the owner yesterday,

00:10:23.200 --> 00:10:25.270
but I am today.

00:10:26.360 --> 00:10:27.480
Explain yourself.

00:10:28.890 --> 00:10:30.880
This shop used to belong to Mr. Wu.

00:10:31.270 --> 00:10:33.120
I was his apprentice, learning the craft.

00:10:33.120 --> 00:10:34.140
But when I got here this morning,

00:10:34.140 --> 00:10:36.030
he suddenly said he was giving it to me.

00:10:36.030 --> 00:10:37.000
And then he left.

00:10:37.440 --> 00:10:38.550
Out of nowhere,

00:10:38.550 --> 00:10:40.150
he just gave it to you, just like that?

00:10:40.150 --> 00:10:41.610
He had no wife or children?

00:10:41.790 --> 00:10:42.990
No wife, no children.

00:10:43.510 --> 00:10:44.760
It’s hard for guys

00:10:44.790 --> 00:10:46.280
in our trade to find a wife.

00:10:46.780 --> 00:10:48.730
As for why he gave it to me,

00:10:48.960 --> 00:10:50.390
he didn't really explain much.

00:10:50.390 --> 00:10:52.840
He just said I own this shop now.

00:10:52.860 --> 00:10:53.720
He gave me the keys,

00:10:53.720 --> 00:10:55.360
packed his things, and left.

00:10:56.910 --> 00:10:59.040
Did you notice anything else unusual?

00:11:01.440 --> 00:11:03.240
Now that you mention it...

00:11:03.910 --> 00:11:05.790
Mr. Wu has been

00:11:07.550 --> 00:11:09.670
acting strange lately.

00:11:16.990 --> 00:11:18.920
Master, the spirit envoy reports—

00:11:19.310 --> 00:11:22.310
there's another murder case
on the outskirts of town.

00:11:26.190 --> 00:11:28.870
Master, there might be
something fishy about this.

00:11:28.870 --> 00:11:30.960
Should we ask
Lord Bai and the others over?

00:11:30.960 --> 00:11:31.960
In his condition,

00:11:32.120 --> 00:11:33.750
one murder case
is enough to wear him down.

00:11:33.750 --> 00:11:34.790
Mother!

00:11:34.890 --> 00:11:36.200
Go check what's wrong quickly.

00:11:36.200 --> 00:11:37.000
Mother!

00:11:37.440 --> 00:11:38.240
Mother!

00:11:39.390 --> 00:11:41.720
Why did you end your life,

00:11:42.080 --> 00:11:44.440
leaving me all alone?

00:11:45.000 --> 00:11:47.320
How am I supposed to live without you?

00:11:48.440 --> 00:11:49.320
Mother!

00:11:51.270 --> 00:11:52.510
Mother!

00:11:54.150 --> 00:11:55.360
Mother!

00:12:05.360 --> 00:12:05.910
Go ahead.

00:12:10.910 --> 00:12:12.360
About five days ago,

00:12:12.840 --> 00:12:15.500
Mr. Wu suddenly
told me to clean the entire shop.

00:12:15.910 --> 00:12:18.970
He even had me climb up
to the roof to sweep away the dust,

00:12:19.270 --> 00:12:21.840
and clean every corner of the stairs.

00:12:22.360 --> 00:12:23.270
Clean it.

00:12:23.720 --> 00:12:24.630
Clean it all.

00:12:25.270 --> 00:12:26.270
Clean it.

00:12:26.750 --> 00:12:27.750
Once it's clean,

00:12:28.150 --> 00:12:29.480
fortune will come to me.

00:12:29.630 --> 00:12:31.030
I want to turn my luck around.

00:12:31.030 --> 00:12:32.430
I want to welcome wealth.

00:12:32.960 --> 00:12:34.560
I want to turn my luck around.

00:12:34.870 --> 00:12:36.270
I want to welcome wealth.

00:12:36.510 --> 00:12:39.510
We cleaned all day that day,

00:12:39.790 --> 00:12:41.360
and Mr. Wu went to bed early.

00:12:42.960 --> 00:12:44.510
He went out at dawn,

00:12:44.870 --> 00:12:46.670
and didn't come back until dusk,

00:12:47.080 --> 00:12:48.080
totally drunk.

00:12:48.910 --> 00:12:50.320
Mr. Wu!

00:12:50.670 --> 00:12:51.480
Be careful.

00:12:53.500 --> 00:12:54.290
Mr. Wu.

00:12:54.750 --> 00:12:55.240
Mr. Wu!

00:12:55.240 --> 00:12:56.000
Bad luck!

00:12:56.510 --> 00:12:58.030
Such bad luck.

00:12:58.200 --> 00:12:59.560
I'm done with this!

00:13:00.390 --> 00:13:02.000
I've made enough money.

00:13:02.510 --> 00:13:03.510
I've made enough.

00:13:04.000 --> 00:13:04.750
And then?

00:13:05.630 --> 00:13:06.440
Then...

00:13:08.080 --> 00:13:08.510
I...

00:13:09.090 --> 00:13:10.160
I forgot.

00:13:10.290 --> 00:13:11.500
Think carefully.

00:13:12.840 --> 00:13:13.960
Then,

00:13:14.670 --> 00:13:17.390
I helped him back to his room.

00:13:18.730 --> 00:13:19.490
Get in bed.

00:13:19.520 --> 00:13:20.570
Get in bed, Mr. Wu.

00:13:24.720 --> 00:13:25.550
Mr. Wu?

00:13:25.790 --> 00:13:28.910
At the time, I felt some kind of urge,

00:13:32.030 --> 00:13:35.870
and that urge compelled me to...

00:13:48.270 --> 00:13:49.330
What are you doing?

00:13:49.840 --> 00:13:51.440
Why are you touching my gold?

00:13:51.960 --> 00:13:53.440
This gold is mine!

00:13:54.000 --> 00:13:56.120
Nothing happened that night,

00:13:57.100 --> 00:13:59.650
but he didn't eat anything the next day.

00:14:00.160 --> 00:14:03.890
He didn't leave the house
until around 9 that night.

00:14:04.440 --> 00:14:06.570
Then he took a bamboo pole and went out.

00:14:06.600 --> 00:14:08.390
Are you sure it was a bamboo pole?

00:14:08.390 --> 00:14:09.470
There's no mistaking it.

00:14:09.470 --> 00:14:12.730
I was planning to use that bamboo
to fix a paper horse's leg.

00:14:14.630 --> 00:14:15.550
And after that?

00:14:21.240 --> 00:14:22.370
Mr. Wu, you're back.

00:14:22.750 --> 00:14:24.680
I'll make the bed for you right now.

00:14:25.450 --> 00:14:27.030
Ji, lie down.

00:14:27.030 --> 00:14:29.120
Lie down. Come here.

00:14:30.730 --> 00:14:31.640
Ji,

00:14:32.080 --> 00:14:34.080
from now on, this shop

00:14:35.000 --> 00:14:36.240
is yours.

00:14:38.080 --> 00:14:38.960
Gold.

00:14:41.960 --> 00:14:44.090
Did your boss have any other business?

00:14:45.390 --> 00:14:47.270
Since he had no other way
to put food on the table,

00:14:47.270 --> 00:14:49.470
this gold must've come from a windfall.

00:14:49.790 --> 00:14:50.270
My Lord,

00:14:51.080 --> 00:14:53.200
the time matches perfectly.

00:14:53.640 --> 00:14:56.970
Wu Youdao went out at midnight
and came back at dawn,

00:14:57.200 --> 00:14:59.630
which happens to be
the time the mute beggar was killed.

00:14:59.630 --> 00:15:01.670
And then there's the murder weapon,
the bamboo pole.

00:15:01.670 --> 00:15:03.310
His shop is full of them.

00:15:03.760 --> 00:15:05.760
And the paste, that matches too.

00:15:06.080 --> 00:15:06.840
I think

00:15:06.840 --> 00:15:09.100
it's highly likely that Wu Youdao did it.

00:15:09.200 --> 00:15:10.460
What about the motive?

00:15:11.510 --> 00:15:14.080
Since Wu Youdao gained a windfall,

00:15:14.270 --> 00:15:15.270
why would he

00:15:16.080 --> 00:15:19.200
kill a beggar he had
absolutely no grudge against?

00:15:21.630 --> 00:15:22.960
There must be something

00:15:23.200 --> 00:15:25.080
we're still missing in this case.

00:15:28.270 --> 00:15:29.000
Walk faster.

00:15:31.360 --> 00:15:31.820
Faster.

00:15:31.960 --> 00:15:32.560
Fengling.

00:15:33.750 --> 00:15:35.600
Where did you get this gold?

00:15:36.960 --> 00:15:38.220
And who is this person?

00:15:39.630 --> 00:15:40.510
Lord Bai.

00:15:41.000 --> 00:15:42.390
My master said

00:15:42.630 --> 00:15:44.630
this case is none of your business.

00:15:45.270 --> 00:15:46.080
Why?

00:15:46.390 --> 00:15:47.650
It's for your own good.

00:15:48.030 --> 00:15:48.630
Aren't you...

00:15:48.630 --> 00:15:49.230
Fengling.

00:15:50.630 --> 00:15:51.510
Lady Fufeng.

00:15:54.120 --> 00:15:54.870
Lady Fufeng.

00:15:55.720 --> 00:15:56.840
No wonder I felt like

00:15:56.840 --> 00:15:58.770
someone was following me earlier.

00:15:59.480 --> 00:16:00.210
So it was you.

00:16:07.390 --> 00:16:08.960
Lord Bai, the way you put it,

00:16:09.870 --> 00:16:12.070
makes it sound like I were stalking you.

00:16:12.200 --> 00:16:13.000
What?

00:16:13.750 --> 00:16:17.150
Is Yin-Yang Crossing only for Lord Bai
to investigate cases,

00:16:17.320 --> 00:16:19.250
and I'm not even allowed to pass by?

00:16:20.320 --> 00:16:21.780
Of course you're allowed.

00:16:26.870 --> 00:16:28.200
You look terrible,

00:16:30.080 --> 00:16:32.280
as if a gust of wind could knock you over.

00:16:34.870 --> 00:16:36.510
Leave this case to me.

00:16:37.320 --> 00:16:38.250
Go back and rest.

00:16:45.870 --> 00:16:46.600
Give it to me.

00:16:48.550 --> 00:16:49.360
Lady Fufeng.

00:16:49.910 --> 00:16:52.240
This case happened in Yin-Yang Crossing,

00:16:52.320 --> 00:16:53.920
and it concerns a human life.

00:16:54.150 --> 00:16:55.320
As the county magistrate,

00:16:55.320 --> 00:16:57.960
finding the truth is my duty.

00:16:58.440 --> 00:16:59.320
No one

00:16:59.390 --> 00:17:01.510
may interfere with my investigation.

00:17:01.510 --> 00:17:02.440
Bai Shanjun.

00:17:02.870 --> 00:17:04.630
When have I ever interfered
with your investigation?

00:17:04.630 --> 00:17:07.359
Don't you realize
what state you are in right now?

00:17:10.390 --> 00:17:11.390
Lady Fufeng.

00:17:12.790 --> 00:17:14.030
This is the first time

00:17:15.030 --> 00:17:16.510
you've spoken this much to me

00:17:16.510 --> 00:17:18.910
about anything other than the case itself.

00:17:20.680 --> 00:17:21.540
Suit yourself!

00:17:22.400 --> 00:17:23.130
My Lady.

00:17:28.000 --> 00:17:29.400
I'm glad that

00:17:30.790 --> 00:17:32.320
you're concerned about me.

00:17:35.160 --> 00:17:35.960
Since I might

00:17:37.130 --> 00:17:39.460
drop dead in the wilderness at any moment,

00:17:40.780 --> 00:17:43.450
please don't be angry with me.

00:17:50.350 --> 00:17:51.080
Is that okay?

00:18:03.240 --> 00:18:04.040
For this case,

00:18:05.640 --> 00:18:07.240
with just my strength alone,

00:18:08.480 --> 00:18:10.400
I'm afraid I may not be able to handle it.

00:18:10.400 --> 00:18:11.200
What if

00:18:16.810 --> 00:18:18.090
you took the lead,

00:18:19.550 --> 00:18:20.610
and I assisted you?

00:18:21.880 --> 00:18:22.640
Is that okay?

00:18:45.960 --> 00:18:46.720
Now,

00:18:48.200 --> 00:18:50.790
can we talk about the matter of the gold?

00:19:02.270 --> 00:19:03.070
Zhao Er.

00:19:03.680 --> 00:19:06.310
Where did you get these three gold ingots?

00:19:07.200 --> 00:19:08.660
I won them fair and square.

00:19:08.720 --> 00:19:09.480
My Lord.

00:19:09.550 --> 00:19:11.350
I had good luck and won some money.

00:19:11.350 --> 00:19:12.720
Does that break the law?

00:19:13.240 --> 00:19:15.830
We've already checked
every gambling house in this county.

00:19:15.830 --> 00:19:17.680
Just last month at Qianjin Gambling House,

00:19:17.680 --> 00:19:18.960
you owed a huge debt.

00:19:19.200 --> 00:19:22.240
Yet, your luck miraculously
turned around in just a few days?

00:19:22.240 --> 00:19:25.440
When and in what kind of game
did you win these gold ingots?

00:19:25.480 --> 00:19:27.310
I won them in the neighboring county.

00:19:27.310 --> 00:19:28.110
What?

00:19:28.350 --> 00:19:30.000
My Lord, you seem to control everything.

00:19:30.000 --> 00:19:31.400
Are you going to control
where I go to make money now?

00:19:31.400 --> 00:19:31.880
You...

00:19:38.270 --> 00:19:38.960
Zhao Er!

00:19:38.960 --> 00:19:39.640
You...

00:19:58.670 --> 00:20:00.120
Say that again.

00:20:02.670 --> 00:20:03.470
My Lord!

00:20:04.070 --> 00:20:05.830
I was wrong!

00:20:08.550 --> 00:20:10.200
I was talking nonsense!

00:20:29.480 --> 00:20:30.000
My Lord.

00:20:30.330 --> 00:20:32.610
My mother left these gold ingots to me,

00:20:32.760 --> 00:20:35.350
said they were passed down
from our ancestors,

00:20:35.350 --> 00:20:38.440
and told me to use them
to pay off debts and live a good life.

00:20:38.440 --> 00:20:40.380
I let greed cloud my judgment just now.

00:20:40.380 --> 00:20:41.440
Please forgive me, My Lord!

00:20:41.440 --> 00:20:43.240
Please forgive me, Lady Fufeng!

00:20:43.350 --> 00:20:44.830
Passed down from your ancestors?

00:20:44.830 --> 00:20:48.720
When and where did your mother

00:20:48.860 --> 00:20:50.390
give you these gold ingots?

00:20:50.880 --> 00:20:52.280
Just yesterday morning,

00:20:52.480 --> 00:20:53.940
right at the break of dawn.

00:20:54.240 --> 00:20:57.000
She said it was
our family's emergency money,

00:20:57.240 --> 00:20:59.440
and said there might be more.

00:21:00.200 --> 00:21:02.460
There might be more? What does that mean?

00:21:02.720 --> 00:21:04.270
I don't know either.

00:21:04.510 --> 00:21:07.110
She just told me to check
beside her pillow the next morning,

00:21:07.110 --> 00:21:08.240
and I'd understand.

00:21:08.630 --> 00:21:10.660
My Lord, everything I said is true.

00:21:10.960 --> 00:21:12.960
That's exactly what my mother said.

00:21:13.070 --> 00:21:14.310
But when I woke up,

00:21:14.480 --> 00:21:15.880
my mother had already...

00:21:16.070 --> 00:21:17.930
already hanged herself, My Lord.

00:21:18.480 --> 00:21:19.870
Before your mother hanged herself,

00:21:19.870 --> 00:21:21.640
was there anything else unusual?

00:21:21.640 --> 00:21:22.440
Unusual?

00:21:24.960 --> 00:21:25.820
Three days ago,

00:21:25.960 --> 00:21:27.350
my mother swept and cleaned

00:21:27.350 --> 00:21:28.720
every corner of the house, inside and out.

00:21:28.720 --> 00:21:30.160
In the past, she only did this

00:21:30.160 --> 00:21:31.310
during festivals.

00:21:32.000 --> 00:21:33.960
Does that count as unusual?

00:21:38.200 --> 00:21:39.530
Sweeping and cleaning?

00:21:44.490 --> 00:21:46.150
This case is too complicated.

00:21:46.200 --> 00:21:47.920
We've investigated for days
and still have no clues.

00:21:47.920 --> 00:21:48.790
Exactly.

00:21:49.160 --> 00:21:50.110
I haven't been home

00:21:50.110 --> 00:21:51.510
to see my wife in days.

00:21:52.680 --> 00:21:54.810
And I have no idea when we'll get a lead.

00:22:00.330 --> 00:22:01.790
Fortune-Turning Master,

00:22:01.920 --> 00:22:03.640
can you continue helping me?

00:22:07.570 --> 00:22:08.310
I'm sorry.

00:22:08.310 --> 00:22:10.160
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

00:22:12.640 --> 00:22:13.400
I'm sorry.